make the fitting and discount tab smaller and put them on the same line. Still in the same line add a new tab called Takedowns (number)
Fitting must increase itself according to type of Blind, the price for fitting is:
Panel Blind = $20;
Vertisheer and Curtains = $30;
Shutters = $100;
Any other blind (ex: roller, vertical, etc) = $10.
Also next to fitting add a tick box for Included. If included is ticked, then Fitting is equal to 0
